# Formatting

Match the project's dprint/ESLint config:

- Indent: 2 spaces
- Line width: 120
- No semicolons (ASI)
- Double quotes for strings
- Trailing commas in multi-line only (smaller diffs)
- Arrow functions: use parentheses around params
